N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 153.2 - Notice of transfer

State Regulations

No such accounts, books, contracts, records, documents and
papers shall be transferred from the principal office of such corporation, company, association, joint-stock association, partnership and person under the
jurisdiction of this commission until notice of such transfer has been filed, in accordance with the requirements of section
3.5
of this Title, to the
commission and approval thereof granted. Notes
